.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-CONTEXT" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.33" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-context \- Print resolved project\-local settings context
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose context [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Print the effective project\-local settings, selected profile, binaries, interpolation variables, and derived runtime paths for the active invocation context.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose context
hpc\-compose context \-\-format json
hpc\-compose \-\-profile dev context
.fi
